Package: BayesTestStreak
Type: Package
Title: Testing Streakiness in Binary Sequences by Bayes Factors
Version: 1.0
Depends:  LearnBayes, ggplot2
Date: 2014-04-08
Author: Jim Albert
Maintainer: Jim Albert <albert@bgsu.edu>
Description: BayesTestStreak contains a collection of functions for comparing consistent and streaky models for a binary sequence using Bayes factors.  The methods are based on the group of spacings between consecutive successes.
License: GPL (>= 2)
